                        <div class="slide__text">
                            <h2 class="slide__text-heading">Shimla</h2>
                            <p class="slide__text-desc">The former summer capital of the British in India, and the present capital of Himachal Pradesh, Shimla has been blessed with all the natural bounties which one can think of. It has got a scenic location, it is surrounded by green hills with snow capped peaks. The spectacular cool hills accompanied by the structures made during the colonial era creates an aura which is very different from other hill.</p>
