			     <h1 class="shead-style text-center" style="font-size: 4em;">HIMACHAL PRADESH</h1>
           <p>As it is named, Himachal is carved out of something very pure, unique and delicate. Standing as the neck of India , it is a northern state in the Himalayas. A mountainous state famous for its hill stations , villages and its natural beauty, it’s also a heaven for mountaineers. The horizon of Himachal sets the tone for the beauty that can’t be explained by words.
            Each and every sense Himachal Pradesh makes is a feeling that can only be felt once someone is  there. Goosebumps are the best ways to explain them. The intricate design of a certain land can only be experienced it can’t be taken away or remade even with the maximum effort involved. Sometimes a question also arises how nature can carve something so beautiful. Well sometimes also the beauty that remains in the mysteries can only be felt by seeing them.
